Package org.hfoss.posit.util

Class Summary
DataPoint DataPoint is supposed to be a generic term for representing data items in posit for maps.
DataSet It stores the information about the program that's parsed from the preferences.xml file.
Date All the date functions go here.
ImageAdapter ImageAdapter for showing images in gallerys and gridviews.
LocationDialog Shows the location dialog with the buttons.
PreferencesHandler Parses the preferences.xml file
SpinnerBindings Everything that needs to be bound to a spinner goes here.
StaticOverlay StaticOverlays over the MapViews based on the given DataPoint objects.
Streamer The class for streaming videos from my server
TextUtils All the text related utilities for parsing, presenting text.
WordWrap WordWrap is a simple word-wrapping class which provides word-wrap either to columns of raw text; or to some number of pixels (given a font).
